Collections and Tables in Stata 17 1 Introduction

Collections and Tables in Stata 17 1 Introduction This tutorial introduces the collection and tables commands used in Stata 17. It includes basic information on creating a custom table from the results of descriptive or modelling commands; modifying the layout of tables and customising content and layout.
